{"tid":674494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好似撞鬼","createTime":"2018-05-22T17:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T06:56:04.000Z","uid":87558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"04c06289ff7cfdb57a3d2ce3f2e010120a23a0cc","tid":674494,"uid":87558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱12點幾左右翻屋企<br />\n加埋我有三個人係度等𨋢<br />\n一個女一個男<br />\n咁我棟樓有35層我就住34啦<br />\n然後我入左𨋢之後㩒完34就企埋一邊<br />\n個女人就乜都無做企左係後面<br />\n個男人就27樓就出左去<br />\n然後到34樓之後我就出𨋢<br />\n但係個女人無出到<br />\n而且我好肯定無聽到任何開屋企門聲<br />\n然後㗎𨋢關門之後成分鐘都無再行過<br />\n我膽粗粗走過去㩒部𨋢<br />\n但係入面一個人都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for1999"},{"pid":"3139e6893ce69cf7929782bc821bbc8d7adeb9c9","tid":674494,"uid":31355,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:27:45.000Z","msg":"可能人地都係住34樓姐 <br />\nBtw 望下你後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e341e07987d178a60083f0d8f840c8c19ac833cb","tid":674494,"uid":187283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"好恐怖"},{"pid":"1b56dde4808ab67dc2bc0c3fc65e9538a170ff9f","tid":674494,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"睇cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727f38312033a547faebcde299e803b4fb6bf6fe","tid":674494,"uid":31522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbfa708fb7992864beedf36b624d34af462e3feb","tid":674494,"uid":87558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"727f38312033a547faebcde299e803b4fb6bf6fe","tid":674494,"uid":31522,"like":1,"dis